<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-13654] optaplanner-7.23 not usable in WildFly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-13654</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;drools-7.23 uses this code in `org.drools.core.common.ProjectClassLoader` ...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; void setDroolsClassLoader(&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;ClassLoader&lt;/span&gt; droolsClassLoader) {
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (getParent() != droolsClassLoader &amp;amp;&amp;amp; isOsgiClassLoader(droolsClassLoader)) {
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;.droolsClassLoader = droolsClassLoader;
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (CACHE_NON_EXISTING_CLASSES) {
                nonExistingClasses.clear();
            }
        }
    }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;drools-7.14 uses&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; void setDroolsClassLoader(&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;ClassLoader&lt;/span&gt; droolsClassLoader) {
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (getParent() != droolsClassLoader) {
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;.droolsClassLoader = droolsClassLoader;
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (CACHE_NON_EXISTING_CLASSES) {
                nonExistingClasses.clear();
            }
        }
    }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In a non flat classpath environment, the later version of drools does not allow the CL to get set to anything that is not an OSGi CL. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;CrossRefs: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/wildfly-extras/wildfly-camel/issues/2831&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/wildfly-extras/wildfly-camel/issues/2831&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/kiegroup/drools/commit/85c5308031a84a0ac4086c1df363bb1b4b3c6af9&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/kiegroup/drools/commit/85c5308031a84a0ac4086c1df363bb1b4b3c6af9&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
